1
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:43,440
Where is this?

2
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,500
Why have I never been here before?

3
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,120
This time,

4
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,840
in front of the princess,

5
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,370
I must really prove myself.

6
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:02,170
So, the Tiger Marquis was the one who betrayed me.

7
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:04,580
But I have to pretend I don't know for now.

8
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:07,320
Where can I find the Copper Frog?

9
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,000
Take that!

10
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:26,940
She is Princess Zhaoyang.

11
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,240
He is the Siamese Prince.

12
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,520
We meet again.

13
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,280
We meet again.

14
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,400
Princess.

15
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:44,079
A day apart feels like three years.

16
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,480
I also

17
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:47,600
missed you dearly.

18
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,720
Are ancient people this forward now?

19
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:53,160
How far have we gone?

20
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:58,900
We aren't married yet,

21
00:02:59,079 --> 00:03:00,680
so we might not be that close.

22
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,000
Why don't you

23
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,240
take a walk with me?

24
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,340
I would be honored.

25
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,490
Don't be afraid.

26
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:33,600
I'll protect you.

27
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:45,600
Actually,

28
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,810
I'm still somewhat useful.

29
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:49,520
Alright.

30
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:52,360
Killing the guards and kidnapping the Princess.

31
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:54,200
How dare you!

32
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,920
Why am I back here?

33
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,360
What's going on?

34
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:09,240
You triggered the AI virtual space's

35
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,360
circuit breaker mechanism.

36
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:13,080
As long as it contradicts the historical process,

37
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,520
everything starts over.

38
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,320
You must find the right way

39
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,649
to let history play out.

40
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:18,880
Otherwise,

41
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:21,600
you'll be stuck in this scenario forever.

42
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,920
History records that

43
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:25,000
the Prince was hunted down here.

44
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:31,440
How dare you.

45
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:34,000
You killed the guards and kidnapped the Princess.

46
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:34,600
Stop.

47
00:04:35,159 --> 00:04:36,159
Are you kidding me?

48
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:37,240
Who is that big oaf?

49
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,320
He is the Tiger Marquis.

50
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,400
Unmatched in martial arts,

51
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:41,000
the Princess's right-hand man.

52
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,680
Bah!

53
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,080
He is the villain who killed me

54
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:45,540
on the night of my wedding.

55
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,520
He is the one who eventually betrayed me.

56
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:49,240
However,

57
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,600
right now, he is still

58
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,260
your most capable assistant.

59
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,159
Through the Tiger Marquis,

60
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:56,020
we can find the first Bronze Frog.

61
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,370
How dare you.

62
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:01,320
Killing guards and holding the Princess hostage.

63
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,440
You have some nerve.

64
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:08,850
Hey, big guy.

65
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:10,220
Don't come any closer!

66
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,850
Pass down the order.

67
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:14,210
The Prince of Siam murdered the Princess,

68
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,040
and I executed him on the spot.

69
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:17,360
Ready the army.

70
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,760
Prepare to flatten Siam at any moment.

71
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:21,360
The Princess isn't dead yet!

72
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,220
Let me tell you,

73
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,360
as long as you hand over

74
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,360
the Glazed Frog in your hand.

75
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,440
I'll release the Princess.

76
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,160
Lord Tiger Marquis,

77
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,120
save me!

78
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,840
Give him the Liuli Frog quickly!

79
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:29,520
Princess.

80
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:31,740
Isn't the Liuli Frog in your hand?

81
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:00,520
How was it?

82
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:06,080
I left the Princess behind all alone.

83
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:06,920
Don't worry.

84
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,120
After you go offline,

85
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,440
the virtual space stops running.

86
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:11,160
There is no concept of time there.

87
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:11,890
That's good.

88
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:13,840
But I have one more thing.

89
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:23,840
Any new discoveries?

90
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:27,240
Did you find the Bronze Frog?

91
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,250
Our speculation was wrong.

92
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:31,480
At this point in time,

93
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:34,280
the Glazed Frog is still with the Princess.

94
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:39,690
If the grand finale is correct,

95
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:42,400
and the Prince did die in Siam

96
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:45,050
at his wedding to the Princess,

97
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,000
then right now,

98
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,980
the Prince shouldn't be dead yet.

99
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,560
According to historical records,

100
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,960
the Glazed Frog will eventually fall

101
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,240
into the hands of Marquis Hu.

102
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,680
So, shouldn't we

103
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,940
let Marquis Hu get the Glazed Frog first?

104
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:01,880
Princess, Prince.

105
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:02,640
I'm coming.
